{"title":"红旗（外一首）","authors":["况明先"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":11,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"况明先"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘扬在我生命的最高处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温暖我的血肉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召唤我的勇气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天穿透我的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我回到那些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰燃烧的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个被鸦片毒坏肌体的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用革命医治创伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从枪口走向黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜艳的一角　从此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染红我的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺满我的瞳仁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲般温柔的甜梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带我跨过无数风雨历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗作为一种象征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严而神圣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗作为一种真理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解释了所有的流血和牺牲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仰视红旗的全部意义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于两个沉甸甸的大字——祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们熟悉火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像农民熟悉季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在燃烧的情感里　让你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"体味一种力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自熔化矿石的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水是他们付出的一部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声滴落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟会使你受到震动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最平凡的流动中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深刻理解奉献"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁是他们收获的果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗糙的表面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会抚出余温"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望跟随刀锋深入"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见闪着光泽的内核"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你与他们交上朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过凸起的胸肌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会真真实实地懂得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与熔炉打交道的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们自己就是一块钢铁"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}